{"tid":583780,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好易俾嘢嚇親？","createTime":"2018-03-07T09:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T11:00:10.000Z","uid":29601,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ee9044c249c6b9bf932e411ebe94ac25b123cc17","tid":583780,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊人哋專登嚇你果啲<br />\n係例如：<br />\n有隻蚊/ 其他昆蟲飛埋嚟或者喺我眼前經過 就嚇到成個人彈一彈&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n屋企附近好多貨櫃車上落會突然勁大聲砰 又係嚇到震一震咁 但望返周圍啲人又無嘢&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n睇電影 已經唔係睇恐怖片 <br />\nDunkirk啲槍聲 砰砰砰 又嚇到彈起 搞到睇呢套戲果陣全程都好緊張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係因為個劇情 而係如果我無心理準備嘅話 又會嚇親 <br />\nGuardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2好記得有一幕唔知邊個拍死隻蜘蛛 我都嚇親 隔離啲frd又無嘢喎 <br />\n次次都係得我一咁樣 好大反應 好柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有無人同我一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗到其他例子再講"},{"pid":"e9646633c15d4168a22c17bd4c6c3c7243995c90","tid":583780,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:42:48.000Z","msg":"打少啲丁"},{"pid":"92cc090dd47cab854a6f37b030fde83fe2c0a324","tid":583780,"uid":22414,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"男人黎? 咁垃圾死左去啦"},{"pid":"3dfef3185ce1d89880b8d685b7af5a29a4bb0d23","tid":583780,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9646633c15d4168a22c17bd4c6c3c7243995c90","tid":583780,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:42:48.000Z","msg":"打少啲丁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T09:46:31.000Z","msg":"關事咩"},{"pid":"d75f3debb237742f6ac8419a724536f68951a88a","tid":583780,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"